content.rendered:
Directed by Shaad Ali.

Written by Gulzar. Sameer Rajda.

Cast Shraddha Kapoor(Tara). Naseeruddin Shah(Gopi Shrivastava). Aditya Roy Kapoor(Aditya). Sarika Singh(Adi’s Sister in Law). Kitu Gidwani(Tara’s Mother). Srishti Shrivastava(Aisha (as Shrishti Shirvastav)). Vibhoutee Sharma(Jennifer). Nikita Grover(Tara’s Friend 1). Balkrishna Doshi(Balkrishna Doshi). Jasmeet Singh Bhatia(Bantee). Sanjay Gurbaxani(Deputy Commissioner Of Police). Vijayant Kohli(Adi’s Brother / Ravi Gunjal). Neeraj Goswami(Adi’s Office Colleague 2). Ramanan Balakrishnan(Jenny’s Father). Amit Shukla(Hawaldar 1). Leela Samson(Charu). Vikram Mehra(Adi’s Office Colleague 4). Geeta Tandon(Scooty Girl). Paul Varghese(Adi’s Office Colleague 3). Anagha Joshi(Pregnant Woman). Prahlad Kakkar(Adi’s Boss). Kerwin Kaizad Baria(Adi’s Niece). Anil Khopkar(Tara’s Tajui). Dinkar Pundlik Gavande(Traffic Cop). Jude Texeira(Henry’s Father). Syed Arif Ali(Tara’s Boss). Anusha Iyer(Tara’s Colleague 2). Nandita Bandyopadyay(Maria). Manav Arora(Adis Office Colleague 1). Adeetya Teckchandani(Henry). Vikram Naru(Doctor). Eesh(Ashok). Fiza Somjee(Tara’s Colleague 1). Francis Olivera(Church Father). Mohammad Iqbal(Hawaldar 2). Rupa Sahay(Taiji). Bolo Ram(Watchman). Pooja Doshi(Tara’s Friend 2). Saagar Shaah(Lodge Receptionist)

Language Hindi.

Producers Chandresh Bhatt. Parth Dholakia. Hiroo Johar. Karan Johar. Apoorva Mehta. Mani Ratnam.

Production Dharma Productions. Madras Talkies.
